\nThe PRD (v1-ui-business-separation.md) is about UI-business separation. The su
ccess criteria says:\n- `make test-mobile-e2e-login` should pass\n- Full E2E sho
uld pass\n\nSo I need to run the E2E tests. The backend might not be running for
